  <ul>
    <li>Tracks leads and customers</li>
    <li>Integrates with most other tools</li>
    <li>Grows with your business</li>
  </ul>

  <p><strong>For Email Marketing:</strong> ConvertKit or Mailchimp</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Automated email sequences</li>
    <li>Customer segmentation</li>
    <li>Easy to use</li>
  </ul>

  <p><strong>For Scheduling:</strong> Calendly or Acuity</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Online booking</li>
    <li>Automatic confirmations and reminders</li>
    <li>Integrates with your calendar</li>
  </ul>

  <p><strong>For Invoicing:</strong> QuickBooks or FreshBooks</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Automatic invoice generation</li>
    <li>Payment tracking and reminders</li>
    <li>Financial reporting</li>
  </ul>

  <p><strong>For Advanced Users:</strong></p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>n8n</strong> - Open source automation (if you're technically inclined)</li>
